Sovereign Debt Risk Rises to Record in Europe, Swaps Show

-- B y   M i c h a e l   S h a n a h a n
-- 
2011-08-26T07:52:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-26/sovereign-debt-risk-rises-to-record-in-europe-swaps-show.html
The cost of insuring European
sovereign debt rose to a record, according to traders of credit-
default swaps.  The Markit iTraxx SovX Western Europe index of swaps linked
to 15 governments increased 7 basis points to 314, according to
Markit Group Ltd.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Shanahan at 
 mshanahan3@bloomberg.net  